This essay by Meike Reichle focuses on the role of gender in peer production. It's title was chosen because it was a reaction to the essay by Michel Bauwens in CTheory, entitled The Political Economy of Peer Production.

Meike Reichle's essay is at http://www.alphascorpii.net/peer-to-peer.html

Michel Bauwens essay is at http://www.ctheory.net/articles.aspx?id=499

